author: seelmann
msg: Changed name. The ampersand doesn't work well. The name is used in context menu, in the warning dialog and in the preference page. A single '&' is interpreted as mnemonic character in the menu, thus only a '_' is displayed in the context menu. A double '&&' is displayed correctly as one '&' in the menu, however as double '&&' in the dialog and in the preference page.
